Dear Cookie:<br><br>
Your may be dirty but not worthless!<br><br>
Maybe we are the &quot;pearls&quot; that have been cast before the swine in that social pig sty called war.<br><br>
I could be wrong (that would be a new experience) But maybe, just maybe I could be...<br><br>
For Example:<br><br>
Art is just a red white and green marble (Mom said that she had lost her marbles!)<br><br>
Toon Sarge is just a rusty ball bearing that fell out of a John Deere tractor....<br><br>
Paul is an M&amp;M (cause Mom thinks he's so-0-0-ooo sweet!)<br><br>
John is an oily bubble from the bottom of the rapids..<br><br>
Tom is a stunted pumpkin...<br><br>
Bob is a rabbit turd (the kind that I sold to Cookie..told him they were smart pills!)<br><br>
Gary is a paint ball (green of course)<br><br>
Cookie is hardboiled (must be a humming bird egg)<br><br>
Geez...am I the only pearl in the bunch??? Naw...I was right the first time...all my Bro's are pearls.  I'm the only one who has a problem...everybody thinks I'm a white bowling ball...but you have to pay to have the big stuff!<br><br>
MTF
